text: Andrey Shakirov (born 3 February 1960) is a Soviet ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Ski jumpers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
